{"tid":868524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有source)香港將會在2020年正式回歸","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T18:36:49.000Z","uid":101154,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b197a23cb771303f6c0c7728b7ce9395e9c5279a","tid":868524,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/19/215952_82823898a80e6d9e2a8cc80c97a4e571.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F19%2F215952_82823898a80e6d9e2a8cc80c97a4e571.png&h=9156644d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊形容，eID如一條鑰匙，第三方獲得市民批准後，可得知需要的數據，如年齡、住址等，他舉例，擁有eID後，就似買酒時毋須出示身份證，商戶已可得知消費者年滿18歲。為加強保安，港府計劃利用至少兩種生物特徵，如指模、虹膜、聲紋、動作等方式核實身份，惟現時未能公布詳情，本港的eID認證平台最快2020年開始運作。事實上，新加坡去年已宣布開發國家數字身分（NDI）系統，計劃於3年內投入運作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高鐵開通之後，再推eID，變相將監控市民合理化<br />\n美其名方便市民，實則與中國社會信用系統接軌<br />\n隨時攞完你資料落黎捉你上大陸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1995337/eID最快後年推%E3%80%80料政府銀行通行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1995337%2FeID%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E5%BE%8C%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%25E3%2580%2580%E6%96%99%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%A1%8C&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a7fe6ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1995337/eID最快後年推%E3%80%80料政府銀行通行</a>"},{"pid":"c559620d9ff7a63a4002f718fa86acf07b9090c5","tid":868524,"uid":101154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"此外，中環、金鐘、銅鑼灣、灣仔、尖沙咀及觀塘，會於今、明兩年安裝400枝多功能智慧燈柱，將設置<span style=\"color: red;\">大量感應器，收集天氣、人流、車流等數據。</span>楊指出，數據愈實時愈有用，透露創科局會提供規格（spec），決定所用的感應器類型及光纖粗幼等，燈柱亦會成為5G發射基站。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他未有正面回應會否安裝閉路電視</span></span>，但指燈柱可看到車牌，亦可幫忙捉賊，又指香港只有2,100公里的路，但登記車輛逾73萬架，如何改善車流：「要有數據才可解決問題。」"},{"pid":"d1ca7d3fb8c4b3ff92447d046149ff3d6203e43f","tid":868524,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"咁喺連登係咁叫支那嗰班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631d7b1e817c02c906182ca0ccacddc4e5781e67","tid":868524,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"有無方法阻止香港滅亡"},{"pid":"18d1b134b2583ae9cb99efd8ebd2615031a44552","tid":868524,"uid":206392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6a7e2695d5cfc4b5e968115527420d1e0e1468","tid":868524,"uid":137063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524713d3632c06f255320371c2e0e9cbe3e48f19","tid":868524,"uid":89015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"DLLM 5G 發射站<br />\n又要幫仆街共狗埋單<br />\n求Samsung 同NEC快啲出新5G spec <br />\n隊爆華為plz<br />\n<br />\n比土共咁種5G station, 容乜易比佢加大功率搞到啲人生腦癌"},{"pid":"2c2894eb536ce0fec53456103bd99394a6742abf","tid":868524,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"正 大家都成為蝗國一份子"}]}